headline: Jack Henry Named One of America's Most Trusted Companies in Forbes Ranking
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) was honored to be included in Forbes' 2025 Most Trusted Companies in America list, ranking 82nd of U.S. public companies with more than 1,000 employees.
